  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Investigation into the capsize and sinking of scallop dredger Joanna C
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Chief Inspector issues Notification of Direction to Prohibit Access to the wreck of Joanna C</p>

  </div>
</div>

